{"type": "article", "id": 5380, "title": "Swatch 2015 春夏系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-20T07:29:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233808eRLrO8v2iBMnoyIP.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t冬日的寒冷还在继续，但瑞士品牌 Swatch 已经等不及要与大家分享今年的春夏风情，推出了 2015 年春夏系列 7 个主题的腕表，「宠物与我」系列将一只只萌宠搬上手腕，鲜艳明丽的卡通形象非常符合春夏的味道；「微风系列」精致而充满女性气息，柔和的色彩拂过腕间，宛若微风；「超跑系列」借助深沉而果断的外观展现奔放的一面，金属材质更显气质。另有「红白蓝」「游戏室」「冲浪季节」「地中海」4 款主题同步推出。定价 1800－5700 元不等，即将上架各零售门店。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233806Jh0nkNcSKos1PVmI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233806OkxFHNVpREesClZt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233806mrj3k8oyRtcIav4S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233807kiCpdwPA2QgSfGK1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233808UYqEChtkKJwSs61Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}